family_movies.title: Family Movies
family_movies.description: Animated adventures and heartwarming classics that the whole family can enjoy.

255739.title: A Monster in Paris
255739.description: Experiments gone wrong and a chemical explosion results in a monster unleashed in Paris, but he might not be as dangerous as everyone thought.

274712.title: Little Bear Movie
274712.description: Inspired by the classic children's book, a young bear and his father go camping and make a new friend who sets them off on a series of adventures.

274818.title: Miss Spider's Sunny Patch Kids
274818.description: Based on the classic children's book series, Little Miss Spider appears all grown up in this new adventure. It's her wedding day to Holley Spider!

283998.title: Soccer Mom
283998.description: A teenager’s mother pretends to be a famous Italian soccer star in order to coach her daughter’s losing soccer team — but can she keep up the act?

299575.title: Alpha And Omega 2: A Howl-Iday Adventure
299575.description: Kate and Humphrey spend their first winter holiday as a family battling bears, doubt, and nature itself as they search for their missing pup, Runt.

300444.title: Agent Cody Banks
300444.description: Cody Banks seems like an average teenage boy, except for one thing: He's a CIA secret agent. Can he balance math homework, girls, and covert ops?

300445.title: All Dogs Go to Heaven
300445.description: After being betrayed by his partner in crime, a dog cons his way out of Heaven to get revenge, teaming up with an orphan who can talk to animals.

300447.title: Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
300447.description: A widowed investor soups up an old racing car and discovers he has given it the ability to fly. He then takes his kids on an unforgettable adventure.

301352.title: Rikki Tikki Tavi
301352.description: Follows a young mongoose who has been adopted by a human British family and finds he’s all that stands between them and two murderous cobra snakes.

301814.title: The Pink Panther 2
301814.description: Inspector Clouseau is back! This time, he's teaming up with a squad of international detectives to stop a globe-trotting thief from striking again.

302753.title: Yours, Mine And Ours
302753.description: A hilarious true story of a widow and widower whose marriage creates a full house of twenty as they blend their families.

303185.title: Tom Sawyer
303185.description: A young Jodie Foster stars as Becky to Johnny Whitaker's Tom in this heartwarming musical rendition of Mark Twain's classic novel.

306915.title: Alpha and Omega: Family Vacation
306915.description: Two canine parents need to enlist the help of various animals when their wild family vacation is interrupted by a group of wolf hunters.

306932.title: Fluke
306932.description: An overworked and neglectful businessman dies in a car accident, only to be reincarnated as a dog. Will he finally bring his family joy?

310149.title: The Secret of NIMH
310149.description: In this animated adventure, a timid mouse seeks help from a colony of intelligent rats to save her family, but the rats have their own problems.

310151.title: Sleepover
310151.description: Before their freshman year in high school, four best friends have a slumber party that turns into a life-changing adventure.

312167.title: All Dogs Go To Heaven 2
312167.description: Charlie and Itchy travel from heaven to Earth, where they meet a runaway boy while on their mission to retrieve the Angel Gabriel's stolen horn.

313748.title: Franklin and the Turtle Lake Treasure
313748.description: Franklin the Turtle joins his aunt and her goddaughter on a quest, aided by a mysterious treasure map, to find a healing talisman for his grandma.

318781.title: A Mile in his Shoes
318781.description: A minor league baseball team needs a new pitcher, and a man with Asperger's syndrome could be the one to change their losing streak.

321110.title: Alpha and Omega 4: The Legend of the Saw Tooth Cave
321110.description: The Alphas and Omegas share a thrilling adventure after Runt discovers the Saw Tooth Cave where he lends a helping paw to a wolf in need.

321133.title: Sea Level
321133.description: When a bamboo shark discovers that humans are stealing eggs from his reef, he sets off on a mission to retrieve the eggs — by leaving the ocean.

321860.title: Fred 2: Night of the Living Fred
321860.description: After Fred's music teacher is replaced, he grows to suspect that the new teacher is a vampire, sending him on a mission with his friends to prove it.

321863.title: Happily N'ever After 2
321863.description: All your favorite characters are back for more hilarity in HAPPILY N'EVER AFTER 2, a twisted fairy tale re-telling of Snow White!

326924.title: Minor Details
326924.description: When the students at a wealthy boarding school start to become mysteriously ill, several teenagers work together to solve the case.

332933.title: Fred 3: Camp Fred
332933.description: After ending up at the wrong summer camp, Fred makes the best of a bad situation and vows to help his fellow campers win the annual games.

334155.title: Igor
334155.description: A mad scientist’s hunchbacked lab assistant enters the Evil Science Fair, dreaming of becoming a mad scientist himself. Can he create a monster?

342037.title: A Second Chance
342037.description: With the help of her coach and teammates, a young gymnast who lacks confidence strives to show up her rival and earn a spot on the national squad.

342061.title: Pants on Fire
342061.description: A teenage boy tells white lies to get what he wants, only to discover that his lies have started to come true — and ruin his life.

342067.title: Zapped
342067.description: A teenager who struggles to adjust to her new stepfamily and school receives some help when a dog training app gives her the power to control boys.

343317.title: Happily N'ever After
343317.description: An alliance of evil-doers looks to take over Fairy Tale Land but when Cinderella takes a dramatic turn and blossoms into the leader of the resistance effort.

348088.title: Adventures of the Wilderness Family
348088.description: The story of a modern, 1970’s family that grew weary of the hassles of city life in Los Angeles and moved to the Rocky Mountains—never to return.

348945.title: Opposite Day
348945.description: When Billy wishes kids ruled the world, adults and children switch roles. But he and his sister soon realize they need to change things back—and fast.

367652.title: Alone for Christmas
367652.description: When his family leaves him alone on Christmas Eve, a dog tries to prevent burglars from stealing his family’s presents in this fun family comedy.

372440.title: A Turtle's Tale: Sammy's Adventures
372440.description: Sammy the sea turtle and his friend, Ray, swim around the world enduring the challenges of the oceans in search of Shelly, the love of Sammy's life.

389495.title: Legally Blondes
389495.description: Elle Woods's twin cousins deal with student politics, school uniforms, boys, and being framed for cheating at an elite California prep school.

398630.title: Tad: The Lost Explorer
398630.description: Tad is a bored construction worker dreaming of a life of adventure until one day he is mistaken for a famous archeologist and that dream comes true.

406637.title: The Wiggles, Wiggle House
406637.description: Join the fun of The Wiggles' House, and open the door to a house full of fun as we raise the roof!

418815.title: The Little Ghost
418815.description: Three kids take a young ghost on the adventure of his after-life to help him see his first sunrise ever!

419118.title: MVP 2: Most Vertical Primate
419118.description: After being booted from his hockey team, Jack the Chimp hits the road where he meets a skateboarder who takes him on a cross-country skate tour.

419119.title: MVP: Most Valuable Primate
419119.description: A junior hockey team finds a surprising new teammate when a chimpanzee that recently escaped from an experimental lab stumbles into their practice.

432261.title: Agent Cody Banks 2: Destination London
432261.description: Adventure is his attitude, as Cody returns, masquerading as a musical prodigy to stop a former teacher gone rogue with an evil plan to rule the world.

435804.title: Raising the Bar
435804.description: Kelly swears off gymnastics after moving to Australia, but is drawn back in to help a new friend compete, helping renew her love of the sport.

438821.title: The Pebble and the Penguin
438821.description: A shy penguin has to work up his courage to find love, and survive a far-flung adventure, when a very special pebble comes falling from the sky.

441247.title: Wish Upon a Star
441247.description: A younger sister wishes to switch places with her popular older sister and the two bickering siblings awaken to find the wish has come true.

441266.title: Cowgirls 'n Angels
441266.description: A group of rodeo trick-riders recruits a young girl to join them and go on tour where she hopes to find her long lost father along the way.

447845.title: Tarzan
447845.description: Tarzan must protect the jungle, and his beloved Jane, from a greedy businessmen who wants to destroy his natural habitat for profit.

448411.title: Alpha and Omega
448411.description: Two wolves upset the social order when the Alpha daughter of the pack leader and a jovial Omega are captured, fall in love, and try to save their kin.

449506.title: Ernest Goes to School
449506.description: Dim-bulb hero Ernest P. Worrell returns as a school janitor, who goes to laughable lengths to obtain his overdue high school diploma.

449507.title: Ernest in the Army
449507.description: Lame-brain Ernest P. Worrell longs to drive a military big rig, so he enlists, totally unprepared for the day that he is sent into combat.

451649.title: CarGo
451649.description: A young car learns the importance of family when he embarks on a mission to rescue his father who’s been sent to be repurposed as junk metal.

451682.title: Agent Fox
451682.description: Agent FOX has a mission: infiltrate a community of rabbits and locate a mysterious artifact, but a case of mistaken identity puts the mission at risk.

453692.title: The Hero of Color City
453692.description: A boy’s crayons go to a magic, colorful land at night, but when one is left behind, a monster threatens their world and that of young imaginations.

457139.title: Super Detention
457139.description: Troublemakers at a superhero school escape from detention to save their fellow students from an evil villain who wants to steal their powers.

463838.title: The Last Unicorn
463838.description: A brave unicorn and a magician fight an evil king who is obsessed with attempting to capture the world's unicorns.

464400.title: A Turtle's Tale 2: Sammy's Escape From Paradise
464400.description: When poachers grab Sammy and Ray and ship them toan aquarium, the turtles hatch a plan to bust out and find their little hatchlings, Ricky and Ella.

465998.title: Where the Red Fern Grows (Pt. 1)
465998.description: During the Depression, a young boy, who longs for a dog his parents can't afford, comes of age through a journey of adventure,tragedy, and love.

466257.title: Rock-a-Doodle
466257.description: A rooster is shunned from the barn when the animals realize his voice doesn’t make the sun rise, but set soon regret it and try to bring him back.

466281.title: Second Chances
466281.description: A crabby horse named Ginger brings newfound joy to a dispirited girl, still recovering from the car accident that killed her father.

466377.title: Masters of the Universe
466377.description: A brave warrior must free a beautiful sorceress imprisoned by an evil ruler, but the key has been hidden on Earth and found by a teenage duo.

466956.title: Thunder and the House of Magic
466956.description: A lost cat finds shelter in the enchanted home of a retired magician but the man’s scheming nephew also has some tricks up his sleeve.

467546.title: All Creatures Big and Small
467546.description: After falling off Noah's Ark, a pair of curious creatures struggle to survive the flood and hungry predators by making it to higher ground.

472182.title: Escape From Planet Earth
472182.description: When a heroic astronaut from a blue-alien planet gets trapped on notoriously dangerous Earth, his overly-cautious brother must rescue him.

473895.title: Mummy, I'm a Zombie
473895.description: In the sequel to "Daddy, I'm a Zombie," the fate of the world falls into the hands of a popular high school girl as she runs for student council.

476672.title: A Cowgirl's Story
476672.description: After a teen girl’s parents are deployed to serve in the Afghanistan War, she and her grandfather help each other with their faith and family bonds.

484419.title: Casper & Wendy
484419.description: While witches and goblins are off to scare the living, Casper the Friendly Ghost spends Halloween night looking for a pal with a pulse.

484421.title: Woody Woodpecker
484421.description: It’s a classic cartoon cavalcade as Woody Woodpecker, Popeye, Felix The Cat, and their pals star in this family-fun movie of animated specials.

485970.title: The Dog Who Saved Summer
485970.description: When Zeus accidentally destroys an important party, he gets sent to obedience school while a trio of bumbling burglars are planning a heist.

486566.title: Over the Top
486566.description: A truck driver attempts to reconnect with his estranged son as he road trips to Las Vegas to compete in an arm wrestling championship.

486887.title: Warriors of Virtue
486887.description: After a young boy enters a strange world, he meets five noble, wise and loyal Kung Foo kangaroos who teach him his own strengths as they fight evil.

486933.title: Step Dogs
486933.description: After the owners of two mismatched dogs get married and move in together, these four-legged foes must team up to defend their home from burglars.

488965.title: The Pink Panther
488965.description: In this remake, the bumbling Inspector Jacques Clouseau tries to solve the murder and theft of a famous soccer coach and his priceless diamond ring.

489500.title: Heaven’s Door
489500.description: A girl mourning the loss of her grandparents and suffering from her parents’ divorce finds a portal to Heaven and is granted miraculous powers.

489502.title: Storm Rider
489502.description: When her father is arrested for fraud, a spoiled teen loses her horse and is sent to live with her testy uncle, but soon bonds with an orphaned colt.

490048.title: Popeye Classic Cartoons
490048.description: Have a laugh with the hilarious Popeye and all his crazy friends. Singa Home Entertainment shares some of the most memorable cartoons.

491388.title: Friends for Life
491388.description: A retired attorney, whose wife’s death left his family shattered, raises four orphaned wolf pups to adulthood - who later pay him back warmly.

496978.title: The Stolen Princess
496978.description: The power of love is put to the test when a beautiful princess is abducted by an evil sorcerer and her valiant knight must battle for her safe return.

501159.title: Shark Bait
501159.description: An aimless young fish, who has fallen head over gills in love, must find his destiny and save his home and dear ones from a big, bullying shark.

501160.title: The Reef 2: High Tide
501160.description: Trained in the skills of sea power, a hero fish must protect his coral terf from a group of sharks who want to destroy his neighborhood reef.

501187.title: Joseph: Beloved Son, Rejected Slave, Exalted Ruler
501187.description: Biblical animated feature about Joseph, favored by his father and sold into slavery by his brothers, and how he became a faithful, forgiving ruler.

501618.title: The Ash Lad: In the Hall of the Mountain King
501618.description: A farmer’s son is on a bounty mission as he joins his brothers’ quest to save a princess from a nasty mountain troll out to destroy the family farm.

505738.title: A Minecraft Ninja Turtle Movie
505738.description: A group of first-person video game characters team with the Ninja Turtles in a series of digital mines to battle evil forces threatening their world.

507867.title: The Pilgrim's Progress
507867.description: Animated tale of a man obsessed with finding truth and escaping a city’s destruction who encounters hardships, foes and victory in his faith journey.

514262.title: Hansel and Gretel
514262.description: Two poor yet feisty children get left in a forest and find a witch’s gingerbread house that they must escape from - or she will gobble them for dinner!

518587.title: Standing Ovation
518587.description: Five friends decide to enter a national music video contest for tweens in this musical comedy about the power of childhood dreams and adventure.

523591.title: Jack and the Cuckoo-Clock Heart
523591.description: A 19th-century man, whose heart was replaced with a clock at birth, is warned to avoid strong emotions, but love seems determined to find him.

523598.title: Rolling Elvis
523598.description: When a 12-year-old boy and cycling fanatic skips school to watch TV, his mother’s punishment is to perform as Elvis Presley in the school talent show.

525071.title: The Ash Lad: In Search of the Golden Castle
525071.description: This sequel finds Princess Kristin and Espen and on a dangerous quest to find a mythical castle’s healing water that will cure her parents’ poisoning.

525180.title: All Roads Lead Home
525180.description: After losing her mom and moving to her grandfather’s farm, a 12-year-old girl bonds with an old horse and dog as she begins to save all living things.

531743.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! The Movie
531743.description: It’s up to young Yugi to gather the courage and utilize his game skills to defeat Kaiba, his powerful rival, as well as a sinister Egyptian mummy.

536035.title: The Secret of Moonacre
536035.description: Thirteen-year-old Maria is sent to live with her oddball uncle, and soon discovers a magical kingdom that needs her help to survive.

536603.title: Baby Geniuses
536603.description: When a scheming billionaire decides to steal the pre-language baby code to take over the world, the little tykes team up and fight back.

537384.title: Blinky Bill: The Movie
537384.description: An adventurous young koala travels across the wild Australian outback, hoping to find his missing father, and learns what it means to be a hero.

537385.title: Cinderella and the Secret Prince
537385.description: During the Royal Ball, Cinderella discovers that the apparent prince is a fake, and she must save the real one, whom a bad witch turned into a mouse.

538002.title: Wild Witch
538002.description: The simple scratch from a black cat unleashes the power of 12-year-old Clara, who becomes a wild witch destined to rid the world of an ancient evil.

542261.title: Kids TV Cartoon Shows
542261.description: 6 adorable animal friends known as The Loco Nuts are a comic treat as they prank each other while also being there for each other in times of trouble.

550792.title: Monster Family
550792.description: At a Halloween costume party, Emma Wishbone and her family fall under the curse of an evil witch who transforms them into real-life monsters.

555283.title: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes: Maximum Overload
555283.description: Spider-Man, Wolverine and other Marvel superheroes take on a mischievous Loki and a team of super villains in an all-new LEGO adventure.

555284.title: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes: Avengers Reassembled!
555284.description: The Avengers are forced to “party” with Ultron when he seeks to disassemble the team and take over the world by hijacking Iron Man's armor.

555285.title: Lego DC Comics: Batman Be-Leaguered
555285.description: Lone wolf Batman turns down Superman’s offer to join the Justice League before the entire squad disappears and leaves him their only hope for rescue.

555641.title: RV
555641.description: In the spirit of bonding with his dysfunctional family, patriarch Bob rents a motorhome for what becomes a madcap road trip to the Colorado Rockies.

555684.title: LEGO Ninjago: Day of the Departed
555684.description: A ninja battles for his freedom on a national day of remembrance for the dead against ghostly foes trying to gain power to remain in Ninjago forever.

562864.title: Russell Madness
562864.description: A Jack Russell Terrier becomes an unlikely pro-wrestling champion, with help from his monkey trainer, when a man inherits his family’s sports arena.

562963.title: The Donkey King
562963.description: When the ruler of Azad City suddenly renounces the throne, a down-on-his-luck donkey wins the nation's first election, and is crowned The Donkey King.

571516.title: Dear Dumb Diary
571516.description: A creative girl daydreams in her diary about what she wishes her life could look like, imagining it could include catchy musical numbers and dances.

573585.title: Journey 2: The Mysterious Island
573585.description: When a young man receives his grandfather’s distress signal from a remote island, he heads off with his stepfather and a helicopter tour team.

573632.title: Camp Cool Kids
573632.description: Two brothers at summer camp have to face-off during the annual games contests, except one is on the bullying team and the other is with the “dweebs.”

574378.title: To the Beat!
574378.description: Twin teen dancers Mia and Mackie become competitors when offered the chance of a lifetime to try out for their favorite pop star’s new music video.

574817.title: Sunny Bunnies - More Magic
574817.description: Five beaming balls of light named Turbo, Big Boo, Shiny, Iris, and Hopper hailed from the sun to entertain preschoolers with amazing sleights of paw.

575089.title: The Fixies: Top Secret
575089.description: Tiny, fun creatures who fix broken gadgets and can only be seen by kids help a boy and a professor to save one of their own who finds superpowers.

575094.title: Fixies vs. Crabots
575094.description: The brilliant scientist friend of the tiny helpers known as the Fixies ends up in a duel with a rival scientist who created her own robot helpers.

576110.title: Norm of the North 2: Keys to the Kingdom
576110.description: On call to New York and the Arctic, Norm must clear his name for a crime he didn’t commit and then stop a company from stealing his kingdom’s ice.

577924.title: Arthur and the Invisibles
577924.description: After his grandfather disappears, a boy enlists the help of mysterious little people to save his family home from emerging real estate developers.

578551.title: BoBoiBoy: The Movie
578551.description: BoBoiBoy and his friends come face-to-face with a greedy alien treasure hunter as they race to rescue their friend, Ochobot, and uncover the secrets behind a powerful ancient 'Power Sphere' on a mysterious island.

579029.title: Pets 2
579029.description: The hilarious trio of animal pals snuggles up on the couch to watch cats being cats in the best way possible: silly, funny, and fierce!

586168.title: Cop and a Half
586168.description: After an observational eight-year-old witnesses a murder, a hard-boiled detective must take the child under his wing to solve the crime.

595780.title: Scales: Mermaids Are Real
595780.description: A young girl faces the bittersweet reality that, on her upcoming twelfth birthday, she is destined to turn into a mermaid.

598882.title: The Cat in the Hat Knows a Lot About Christmas!
598882.description: Be our guest to help poor baby reindeer Ralph get his wish to spend Christmas with his family in the far-off land of Freeze-Your-Knees.

605473.title: Maya the Bee Movie
605473.description: A bubbly little bumblebee rebels against the rules of the hive to make all kinds of friends—from violin-playing grasshoppers to a hornet named Sting.

605770.title: Maya the Bee 2: The Honey Games
605770.description: Following an unproductive harvest season, it’s up to Maya and her brave friends to save their hive by competing in a series of games.

607451.title: E.T. The Extra-Terrestrial
607451.description: A boy forms a special bond with a sweet and gifted alien from another planet. He tries to keep it a secret, but he needs help to keep the visitor safe.

609721.title: The Karate Kid
609721.description: Jaden Smith stars in the 2010 reboot of the iconic franchise, this time as a young arrival in China who learns self-defense from a karate master.

611638.title: Son of Bigfoot
611638.description: A teen longs to know his father and sets out on the adventure of a lifetime to find out who he is- only to learn that his old man is Bigfoot!

611824.title: Luis and the Aliens
611824.description: A boy at risk of being sent to boarding school due to his neglectful Dad - and three aliens stranded due to watching too much TV - must help each other out.

615215.title: Playmobil: The Movie
615215.description: When her little brother goes missing, Marla heads to a magical animated world where she teams up with a secret agent and truck driver to find him.

616016.title: Tales of a Fifth Grade Robin Hood
616016.description: A boy in an under-funded school finds the vice principal is stealing money from their fundraisers, so he organizes his friends to get the money back.

617602.title: Swimming for Gold
617602.description: A former US women’s swim team star suffers an injury that forces her to reevaluate her dreams and brings her to coach the Australian men’s swim team.

619497.title: Miracle Dogs
619497.description: Based on true events, Josh learns about love, loss, and optimism when he looks for homes for abandoned puppies with healing effects on humans.

634430.title: The Healer
634430.description: With the help of a teenage girl with terminal cancer, Alec Bailey learns to embrace and put to use his family’s mysterious gift of healing people.

637037.title: Wheely
637037.description: Cartoon adventure about an underdog cab car trying to be the King of the City in an imaginary world where cars are the only citizens.

638180.title: To the Beat: Back 2 School
638180.description: In this sequel, sisterhood is tested, new friends are made, and rivalries pop up as the students compete for a prestigious, paid summer scholarship.

638244.title: Top Cat Begins
638244.description: After hatching a plot to steal from Mr. Big, Top Cat and Benny are forced on the run and rally their pals to help finally dethrone the reptilian ruler.

639949.title: The Snow Queen 3: Fire and Ice
639949.description: A young woman raised amongst trolls leaves the comfort of her warm home to find her parents and prevent an impending global disaster.

647476.title: Aliens in the Attic
647476.description: With their parents none the wiser, siblings must stop a band of tiny aliens from invading the basement of their vacation home and conquering Earth.

647479.title: Sister Act 2: Back in the Habit
647479.description: A Las Vegas showgirl-turned-singing nun becomes a run-down Catholic school’s only hope of reviving its music program and keeping its doors open.

648919.title: Orphan Horse
648919.description: A runaway from a stressed foster home is given shelter by the rancher whose barn she took shelter in – if she’ll work with his orphaned young horse.

649752.title: Sheep & Wolves
649752.description: After a wolf is transformed into a sheep, he must work hard to gain the friendship of his fellow sheep to protect him from vicious wolf attacks.

652270.title: The Goonies
652270.description: A pair of brothers hope to save their house by following a treasure map and taking their friends along on a subterranean sea adventure.

654077.title: Leap!
654077.description: An ambitious orphan with dreams of becoming a ballerina makes her way to the Paris Opera where she auditions for the lead in "The Nutcracker.”

654882.title: Judy Moody and the Not Bummer Summer
654882.description: Based on the hit children's book series, a third-grader makes her own fun for the summer after her initially fabulous plans don't come together.

655363.title: We Bought a Zoo
655363.description: A single dad set out to give his family a fresh start by uprooting them to the Southern California country to a home in the middle of a neglected zoo.

655369.title: The Monkey King Reborn
655369.description: Monkey King is in a race against time to rescue Tang Monk before the King of Demons regains power and initiates his plan to destroy the Earth.

661453.title: The Legend of the Five
661453.description: A group of misfit teenagers find a relic, which transports them to a magical forest where they must stop an age-old evil from destroying the world.

666560.title: Bilal: A New Breed of Hero
666560.description: When Bilal and his sister are abducted and thrown into a world of injustice, he finds the courage to make a change. Inspired by true events.

670339.title: I Believe
670339.description: After coming across a bible verse outside of a church, a 9 year old boy finds supernatural power behind God's message in the form of miracles.

671658.title: Alice in Wonderland
671658.description: When a young girl falls asleep in a meadow, she dreams of entering a magical fantasy land filled with strange adventures and magical creatures.

672233.title: The Little Mermaid
672233.description: A journalist and his niece must save a mermaid who’s being held captive by the evil Locke, as she is the key behind the magical potion they seek.

675043.title: The Indian in the Cupboard
675043.description: Magic enters the life of a Brooklyn boy on his ninth birthday upon receiving an old wooden cupboard, a set of antique keys and a toy Indian figurine.

675108.title: Seventeen Again
675108.description: When Willie's science experiment goes awry, it sends both of his grandparents back to their youth. Can he find a way to reverse the process?

675668.title: Sgt. Stubby: An American Hero
675668.description: A stray dog joins his new master on the battlefields of the First World War. Through his valor, he becomes the most decorated dog in American history.

676858.title: 16 Wishes
676858.description: On her 16th birthday, Abby Jensen's every wish comes magically, wondrously true until one wish too many go wrong and alters everything.

681932.title: Kindness Matters
681932.description: A puppy left behind in a dumpster connects the lives of a lonely recluse and a bullied young boy with a speech impediment and vivid imagination.

682075.title: Switched
682075.description: Tired of being bullied, Cassandra prays that her nemesis, Katie, the queen bee of social media, would know what it's like to walk a day in her shoes.

682797.title: Casper
682797.description: Seeing is believing in this adventure about a kind spirit in need of a friend and his ghostly uncles who want all “fleshies” out of their manor.

689820.title: Max Winslow and the House of Secrets
689820.description: Five teenagers compete to win a billionaire scientist's mansion by facing off against the super computer that controls it.

690283.title: Golden Shoes
690283.description: With his father missing in action and his mother in the hospital, a young boy consoles himself with dreams of playing in the youth soccer league.

691608.title: Rock Dog 2: Rock Around the Park
